“I really like it. We are talking about an everyday car that you can take to the track to have a lot of fun”
Kimi’s words leave no doubts: the new GTAm, the ideal mix for use every day and on the track, is finally ready.
#AlfaRomeo #GiuliaGTAm @alfaromeoracingorlen @kimimatiasraikkonen
